  <glossary>
    <title>Glossary</title>
    <glossentry><glossterm>Patch</glossterm>
      <glossdef>
	<para>A patch is like a function.
	      It is named after the patches in the first
	      modular sound synthetizers.</para>
      </glossdef>
    </glossentry>
    <glossentry><glossterm>Patchwork</glossterm>
      <glossdef>
	<para>A patchwork is a directed graph of patches.</para>
      </glossdef>
    </glossentry>
   </glossary>